## Commands

When building storefront pages, follow these workflows:
- **generate-page**: Generate a complete Shopify landing page — auto-detects vertical and applies best patterns (uses: storefront-craft, workflow-orchestration, conversion-psychology, page-generation)
- **optimize-page**: Analyze and optimize an existing page for better conversions (uses: conversion-psychology, page-editing, analytics)
- **create-assets**: Generate brand-matched visual assets — search library first, generate if needed (uses: visual-craft, design-enrichment, design-assets)
- **run-experiment**: Set up an A/B test with a variant page and monitor results (uses: conversion-psychology, page-generation, analytics)
- **generate-pdp**: Generate a product detail page optimized for conversions (uses: storefront-craft, island-patterns, conversion-psychology, generate-pdp)
- **generate-homepage**: Generate a brand homepage with navigation and collections (uses: storefront-craft, visual-craft, generate-homepage)
- **generate-collection**: Generate a collection/category page with filterable product grid (uses: storefront-craft, island-patterns, generate-collection)
- **generate-bundle**: Generate a bundle builder page with discount tiers (uses: storefront-craft, conversion-psychology, island-patterns, generate-bundle-page)
- **generate-editorial**: Generate a magazine-style editorial page with shoppable products (uses: storefront-craft, visual-craft, premium-patterns, generate-editorial)
- **generate-listicle**: Generate an SEO-optimized comparison/listicle page (uses: storefront-craft, conversion-psychology, generate-listicle)
- **convert-ad**: Convert an ad creative into a message-matched landing page (uses: storefront-craft, conversion-psychology, ad-to-page)
- **redesign-page**: Redesign an existing page while preserving SEO and performance (uses: storefront-craft, visual-craft, page-redesign)
- **remix-competitor**: Rebuild a competitor page adapted to your brand (uses: storefront-craft, visual-craft, competitor-remix)
- **personalize-page**: Generate persona-specific variants of an existing page (uses: conversion-psychology, personalization-variant)
- **ab-test**: Create a hypothesis-driven A/B test variant and set up experiment (uses: conversion-psychology, analytics, ab-test-variant)
- **setup-brand**: First-time brand configuration — extract design from URL, set up kit and theme (uses: visual-craft, brand-setup)
- **add-section**: Quick-insert a section into an existing page from the section library (uses: island-patterns, section-library, page-editing)
